---
title: Louisiana Cannellini Bean Fritters & Wedges with Creamy Slaw & Onion Chutney
description: Fritters don’t get the jitters when it comes to flavour prowess. They storm ahead, raise their head high and arrive
at the table packed with Louisiana spices, Cheddar cheese and cannellini beans. Serve them with a punchy onion
chutney because they deserve nothing less than the best.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
